o a particular field of lore, diagrams and notes on gnomish contraptions, or just about anything else that can be represented using text or pictures. A <i>book</i> of spells is a @item[spellbook|phb].</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","quantity":1,"weight":5,"price":25,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":false,"damage":{"parts":[]},"details":{"description":"<p>A book might contain poetry, historical accounts, information pertaining to a particular field of lore, diagrams and notes on gnomish contraptions, or just about anything else that can be represented using text or pictures. A book of spells is a @Compendium[dnd5e.items.LBajgahniRJbAgDr]{Spellbook}.</p>"},"proficient":true,"attuned":false,"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"range":{"value":0,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"armor":{"value":null,"dex":null}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"SJgpix6pxi5ec5xa":3},"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"items.html","source":"PHB","hash":"book_phb"}}},{"_id":"YwsApkQbK0lE28Fx","name":"Ink (1-ounce bottle)","type":"loot","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/backpack.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p><i>Ink</i> (1-ounce bottle)</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":10,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":false,"attuned":false,"damage":{"parts":[]}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"SJgpix6pxi5ec5xa":3},"flags":{"srd5e":{"page":"items.html","source":"PHB","hash":"ink%20(1-ounce%20bottle)_phb"}}},{"_id":"grrAFYiUdOUdLfy6","name":"Ink Pen","type":"loot","img":"icons/commodities/materials/feather-red-.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0.02,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":false,"damage":{"parts":[]},"proficient":true,"attuned":false,"consume":{"type":"","target":"